stateDiagram-v2
    note right of [*]
        MCP問題根本原因修正タスク
        6件の根本原因を修正するプロセス
    end note

    %% === BUG-2: 密度計算フロー ===
    state "密度チェック開始" as DensityStart
    state "セクション内容解析" as AnalyzeSection
    state "構造行をカウント" as CountStructural
    state "有効行数を算出" as CalcEffective
    state "密度を計算" as CalcDensity
    state "密度判定処理" as EvaluateDensity
    state "密度チェック完了" as DensityEnd

    DensityStart --> AnalyzeSection: コンテンツ取得
    AnalyzeSection --> CountStructural: 各行を確認
    CountStructural --> CalcEffective: 構造行を除外
    CalcEffective --> CalcDensity: 新しい計算式
    CalcDensity --> EvaluateDensity: 密度が基準値以上か
    EvaluateDensity --> DensityEnd: 判定完了

    %% === BUG-3: mkdirパス検証フロー ===
    state "mkdirコマンド受信" as MkdirReceive
    state "パス文字列を抽出" as ExtractPath
    state "パス正規化処理" as NormalizePath
    state "許可プレフィックス照合" as MatchPrefix
    state "許可判定" as EvaluatePath
    state "mkdir実行許可" as AllowMkdir

    MkdirReceive --> ExtractPath: コマンド解析
    ExtractPath --> NormalizePath: パス変換
    NormalizePath --> MatchPrefix: docs/workflows/と比較
    MatchPrefix --> EvaluatePath: マッチしたか
    EvaluatePath --> AllowMkdir: 許可決定

    %% === SEC-ENV-1: インライン環境変数検出フロー ===
    state "コマンド文字列受信" as CmdReceive
    state "正規表現でパターン抽出" as ExtractPattern
    state "環境変数リストと比較" as CheckSecurityVars
    state "危険な変数検出" as DetectDangerousVar
    state "コマンドブロック" as BlockCommand

    CmdReceive --> ExtractPattern: VAR=value検索
    ExtractPattern --> CheckSecurityVars: NODE_OPTIONSなど確認
    CheckSecurityVars --> DetectDangerousVar: セキュリティ変数か
    DetectDangerousVar --> BlockCommand: ブロック処理

    %% === SEC-TIME-1: トークン検証フロー ===
    state "セッショントークン受信" as TokenReceive
    state "トークン長チェック" as CheckTokenLength
    state "Bufferに変換" as ConvertBuffer
    state "timingSafeEqual実行" as CompareTiming
    state "タイミング安全な比較完了" as TokenCompareEnd

    TokenReceive --> CheckTokenLength: 長さ確認
    CheckTokenLength --> ConvertBuffer: UTF-8バッファ化
    ConvertBuffer --> CompareTiming: 定時間比較
    CompareTiming --> TokenCompareEnd: 結果返却

    %% === SEC-LOG-1: ログマスキング処理フロー ===
    state "ログ記録実行" as LogRecord
    state "コマンド文字列取得" as GetCommand
    state "機密パターン検索" as SearchPattern
    state "パスワード置換" as ReplacePassword
    state "APIキー置換" as ReplaceAPIKey
    state "マスキング完了" as MaskComplete

    LogRecord --> GetCommand: コマンド取得
    GetCommand --> SearchPattern: 正規表現マッチ
    SearchPattern --> ReplacePassword: --password=***
    ReplacePassword --> ReplaceAPIKey: API_KEY=***
    ReplaceAPIKey --> MaskComplete: ログ記録

    %% === 全体フロー ===
    state "修正開始" as Start
    state "修正実行中" as Running
    state "修正検証" as Verification
    state "修正完了" as Complete

    Start --> Running: 全6件の修正
    Running --> DensityStart: BUG-2開始
    Running --> MkdirReceive: BUG-3開始
    Running --> CmdReceive: SEC-ENV-1開始
    Running --> TokenReceive: SEC-TIME-1開始
    Running --> LogRecord: SEC-LOG-1開始
    DensityEnd --> Verification: BUG-2完了
    AllowMkdir --> Verification: BUG-3完了
    BlockCommand --> Verification: SEC-ENV-1完了
    TokenCompareEnd --> Verification: SEC-TIME-1完了
    MaskComplete --> Verification: SEC-LOG-1完了
    Verification --> Complete: 全修正検証完了
